Actually it works fine.  Read the .nfo carefully:-  

the app is sensitive to certain words like keygen being displayed anywhere in open windows.  Close all your open WINRARs (and other windows, to be sure to be sure to be certain :) 
Now try the keygen and presto.  This worked for me after I tried these steps anyhow.

Friedkiwi

it'll work fine if you do this: 

install program then place the keygen onto your desktop 

.. close all windows & apps then run sfv checker 

.. click on register 

.. pick a name 

.. run your key gen 

.. copy/pastes the short # onto the space specified 

.. then copy/paste the long code [here's where it's tricky & messed up a couple of times ... you have to drag your pointer across the whole code bc it's so long it doesn't fit in the  keygen window .. so you don't see the whole thing & end up not getting it all]

.. done
